bitcoinclassic (1.2.0-trusty1) trusty; urgency=medium

  * Change block-size strategy to use market size-equilibrium.
  * Include experimental adminserver, disabled by default.
  * Updated flexible-transactions, still disabled.
  * Removed BIP109 signalling and handling.

 -- Tom Z <tomz@freedommail.ch>  Tue, 5 Jan 2017 10:00:00 +0100

bitcoinclassic (1.1.91-trusty1) trusty; urgency=medium

  * Introduce flexible-transactions
  * Introduce xthin-block relay
  * stop shipping libconsensus
  * Make first sync much cheaper with auto-checkpointing
  * Introduce setcoinbase / generateaddress RPC calls
    This removes the requirement for a mining node to have a wallet.
  * Upgrade to use C++11
  * Remove p2p alert handling
  * Fix translation (#184)
  * Allow nodes to accept version2 tx

 -- Tom Z <tomz@freedommail.ch>  Tue, 20 Sep 2016 10:00:00 +0100

